data.title: Sussex Farm Museum (Horam)
data.meta_description: Sussex Farm Museum is a museum in Horam. View visitor information, information about the collection and read reviews.
data.text:
Sussex Farm Museum is a museum in Horam, Heathfield. The museum features exhibits related to Toys and Hobbies, Agriculture, Social History and Industry.
